</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hjGZqJ gtgMXo pf-111_ pf-text-1"><strong>Engage stakeholders early</strong> - Ensure that staff, residents, families, and regulatory bodies are involved in the adoption process from the beginning.
